Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.39,0:00:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.95,0:00:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是汽車爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.25,0:00:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個複雜的大人世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.23,0:00:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清事實的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.71,0:00:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.97,0:02:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽車爆炸事件的真相（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.93,0:02:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸那麽專心在看著什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麽 只是想起以前一些往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.18,0:02:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的銀行裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.32,0:02:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會有個市民公佈欄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.19,0:02:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如有沒有人想養小貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.68,0:03:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也試過在那裏張貼傢庭教師的紙條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 叔叔以前是傢庭教師嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 我完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲當時沒錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.90,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你媽媽在學生時代又結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須一邊打工一邊讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到爸爸你們以前那麽可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想可憐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是讓叔叔教導過的那些學生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.98,0:03:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.22,0:03:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我可是個很出色的教師啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.25,0:03:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據就是讓我教了三年的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來成功考上城南大學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.60,0:03:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我記得她的傢就在米花町
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.96,0:03:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來 讓我帶你們去見小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.61,0:03:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣住在米花町
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻很少來這個地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻和以前一樣沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真的很久沒見過那個人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她叫做田中惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父親是個律師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次上完課都會請我喝啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 所以才會連續教了三年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那輛車怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎麽這樣子開車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麽窄的路還開這麽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了那個賣香煙的店鋪後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她傢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.16,0:04:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個惠小姐該不會已經結婚離開這裏了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.20,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許 也許可能還是單身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你別動歪腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 帶著小孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經長怎麽大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.81,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.69,0:05:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.66,0:05:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.28,0:05:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹 寬美在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 你說寬美她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 滅火器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來 讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.76,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情發生的這麽突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.12,0:06:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你的心情還不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我可以問幾個問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.83,0:06:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.27,0:06:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是崎原惠 沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爆炸中死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.54,0:06:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中寬美 是你的妹妹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.85,0:07:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子上面被裝了爆炸物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.50,0:07:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是炸藥和引爆裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都被裝在車子底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能如果輪子一動的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會自動爆炸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.45,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我記得車子在倒退的瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子就爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崎原小姐 請控制一下情緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再問幾個問題就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.39,0:07:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢是你的父母傢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.42,0:07:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母在半年前因爲交通意外死亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.73,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 之後就只有妹妹一個人住在那裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.42,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車子是你妹妹的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.75,0:07:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我今天從西玉開回父母傢的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲妹妹的車子送去保養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就把車子開進車庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.74,0:08:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我因爲不大會倒車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹 妹妹她說幫我開出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.40,0:08:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽那輛車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本應該是你在上面的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.51,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而犯人卻誤將你妹妹給…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 到底發生什麽事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.11,0:08:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.76,0:08:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐 你從西玉回來的時間大概是幾點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.02,0:08:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午 還沒到2點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候車子有沒有什麽問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.35,0:08:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾點回到娘傢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是2點半左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.81,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸時間正好3點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.25,0:08:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說在這30分鍾之內被人裝上爆炸物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道誰是犯人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有跟人結過怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個星期前 在我傢附近的超市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.39,0:09:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經被一個陌生男子跟蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陌生男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我假裝沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻覺得很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記得那個男人長什麽樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他的樣子很特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.07,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找畫師過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候請你幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.22,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 想不到會在這種情況下和你碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.78,0:10:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道毛利老師現在是個出名的偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.65,0:10:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常常在朋友面前誇燿毛利偵探是我的傢庭教師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.63,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會找出那個害死寬美的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到她會是你的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.18,0:10:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她妹妹你也認識吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 當時她還是個中學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.30,0:10:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常端紅茶和蛋糕進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.95,0:10:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和內嚮的小惠不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個喜歡開玩笑 有很多朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有主見 很精神的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到現在好像也沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐在大學畢業後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在股票公司上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就和一個同事結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒有小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.79,0:11:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她每天都過著傢庭主婦的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而寬美小姐在短大畢業後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在打零工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.19,0:11:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30歲了還是要父母照顧的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於寬美小姐的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.75,0:11:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官 畫像已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 像不像那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.78,0:11:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.57,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要去小惠小姐傢的途中高速行駛汽車的駕駛者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是戴著眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他的發型和下巴完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽你這樣講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽時候看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達小惠傢前10分鍾左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從她傢距離500公尺的窄巷中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.59,0:12:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是他裝完炸彈後正要逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記得他的車牌號碼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.07,0:12:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅色的RV 新宿車牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我馬上去調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.17,0:12:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小惠 我太太小惠她現在情況如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 你是崎原和夫先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.99,0:12:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警局打電話來說我妻子遇到爆炸事件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問現在怎麽樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.05,0:12:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心 你太太沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.02,0:12:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.88,0:12:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你太太的妹妹卻死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬…寬美她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.29,0:12:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 寬美小姐她 爲什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.15,0:12:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夫人的車上被裝了炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而寬美小姐替她開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.64,0:13:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崎原先生 你看過這個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的樣子很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.89,0:13:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場的調查已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.21,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那畫像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.77,0:13:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利他們在現場附近看過他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很有利了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.91,0:13:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在佐藤警官擔當的案子中好像看過這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 我記得她是新宿區的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也只看過一眼而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.18,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張畫和那死者的丈夫很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你馬上拿這張畫像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去聯絡佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.02,0:14:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.85,0:14:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看過他本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是被害者晚上到便利商店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.53,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買東西回傢途中被人用刀刺中的丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.82,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做高橋弘昌 33歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在化學藥品公司上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.15,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位就是他的太太高橋佐知子 27歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從他殺方面正在調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還有個高額的人壽保險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲他的丈夫欠了一筆債
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能因此作案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高橋的車子是不是紅色的RV車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.18,0:15:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿區的車牌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.99,0:15:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.18,0:15:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們看到的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.56,0:15:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以肯定就是高橋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還在化學藥品公司上班的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是很容易可以拿到爆炸物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上遇害事件與爆炸事件是完全不同類型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事件會有關聯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今天的事件中的有關係者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和高橋太太的事件沒有相同人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.85,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是碰巧也太偶然了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這個之外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的徽章好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的交換吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 這並不是徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我換嘛 交換嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.87,0:16:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.72,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 人傢不是說不能換的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.87,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 交換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是交換殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.12,0:16:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個事件就可以連在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個意思嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.18,0:16:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在崎原和夫和高橋弘昌中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個交換殺人的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.27,0:16:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先崎原將高橋的妻子佐知子給殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後輪到高橋去殺害崎原的妻子惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.26,0:16:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當崎原在醫院看到高橋的畫像時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯的震驚了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.04,0:16:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲他早就知道犯人是高橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.85,0:16:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.50,0:16:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是崎原先生爲什麽要殺害惠小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.82,0:17:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當他知道死亡的是妹妹時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然沖出口的那句話可以證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬…寬美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的關係不只是妻子妹妹的關係那麽簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就從這條線進行調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是高橋先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的樣子好像很慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你要去哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.98,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以嫌疑犯的身份將你逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.97,0:17:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的行李裏面有爆炸物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.94,0:18:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崎原看到那張畫像之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.10,0:18:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知高橋趕快躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻給我們逮個正著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崎原也承認自己和高橋聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.37,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出是他殺了高橋的妻子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在酒吧認識高橋的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.02,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出了交換殺人的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後他們就沒再見過面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都已電話做聯係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了不留下證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是用公共電話打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.81,0:18:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是崎原在自己的書房裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一部自己專用的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.79,0:18:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情都會用那部電話聯係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以惠小姐才沒有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.07,0:18:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽崎原的動機是什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你想的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崎原和惠小姐的妹妹寬美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很親密的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.09,0:18:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬美想要開店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而崎原爲了開店的資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.74,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會想到殺害惠小姐的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要惠小姐死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.82,0:19:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的遺産和保險金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.22,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都歸崎原所有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了 惠小姐太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠知道這些事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.73,0:19:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始的時候還不太敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是事實之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裏一直哭泣著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.59,0:19:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只自己的丈夫出軌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.58,0:19:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被自己的妹妹給出賣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過幾天我再去慰問她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.86,0:19:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 事件總算是解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身爲以前的教師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好的安慰她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.09,0:20:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 下次見 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.67,0:20:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件真的解決了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.86,0:20:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像遺漏了些什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和惠小姐不是約好1點鍾的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 早來了一個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.98,0:20:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去喝杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.21,0:20:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這裏不是惠小姐發現高橋在跟蹤她的超市嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.60,0:20:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.98,0:20:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.75,0:20:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 爸爸 那不是惠小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.91,0:21:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.47,0:21:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.88,0:21:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.27,0:21:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽狹窄的空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能輕易的倒車出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.53,0:21:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候惠小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我不大會倒車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.78,0:21:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹她說願意幫我倒車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.66,0:21:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在根本看不出來她是不會倒車的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.74,0:21:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽她爲什麽要寬美小姐幫她倒車呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.69,0:21:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲這樣 車子爆炸而死的寬美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是巧合的不倖嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.52,0:22:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.86,0:22:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果惠小姐知道所有事情的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事件 還沒有結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.79,0:23:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說小惠和這個事件有關嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.00,0:23:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔認識的是高中時代的惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.25,0:24:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入社會後 惠小姐也許改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.51,0:24:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.04,0:24:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.51,0:24:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔心裏很想這麽認爲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.25,0:24:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 事實上她已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.81,0:24:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.57,0:24:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽車爆炸事件的真相（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.80,0:24:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.02,0:24:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.76,0:24:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回事件將會解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.18,0:24:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀情和推理一起完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.41,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開所有雜誌還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.76,0:00:25.38,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭歎息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.64,0:00:29.74,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有適合我的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.89,0:00:33.80,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.11,0:00:37.85,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都無法討得你的歡心 惹得你滿腔怒火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.64,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很抱歉如臨深淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.78,0:00:46.48,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.95,0:00:50.61,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖慾墜的感覺有什麽不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.60,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也一定要嚮前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.00,0:00:59.27,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢 一點也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.22,0:01:08.32,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到緊要關頭不出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.43,0:01:12.12,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 不要用冷淡的眼光看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.94,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我用自己的速度前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.31,0:01:20.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我馬上會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.65,0:01:24.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.14,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖慾墜的感覺有什麽不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.58,0:01:32.68,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也一定要嚮前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.00,0:01:37.31,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢 一點也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.88,0:22:30.52,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這孕育著神秘的夜裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.05,0:22:35.19,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請閉上眼睛 獻上你的祈禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.97,0:22:41.53,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這月光融融的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.10,0:22:47.95,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說我們因爲愛而生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.45,0:22:59.22,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 一切都停滯不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.83,0:23:05.51,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看未來化爲碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.79,0:23:14.22,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 赤著腳 踩在大地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.34,0:23:19.65,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越彩虹 抓住天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.43,0:23:26.17,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈禱 抓住胸前的十字架 在白天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.31,0:23:32.49,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望照燿著你 在夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.61,0:23:38.67,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖的光芒 將你擁抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.82,0:23:45.41,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠爲你停留 爲你的愛而停留
